comment0.text=\r\n\ Qu\u1EA3n\ l\u00FD\ c\u00E1c\ tr\u1EA1ng\ th\u00E1i\ logic\ c\u1EE7a\ Wave\ trong\ d\u1EF1\ \u00E1n\ Golden\ Spatula.\r\n\ Lu\u1ED3ng\ v\u1EADn\ h\u00E0nh\:\ \r\n\ Xong\ Wave\ ->\ \u0110\u1EE3i\ 3s\ ->\ Nh\u1EADn\ Sun\ ->\ \u0110\u1EE3i\ 3s\ ->\ Dave\ n\u00F3i\ ->\ \u0110\u1EE3i\ 5s\ ->\ Augment\ ->\ \u0110\u1EE3i\ 3s\ ->\ Wave\ m\u1EDBi.\r\n
